com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium

Interface WebStorage


  • public interface WebStorage
    The WebStorage interface of the Web Storage API provides access to the session storage or local storage for a particular document on the loaded web page, allowing you to for example add, modify or delete stored data items.
    Web Storage API的WebStorage接口提供对已加载网页上特定文档的会话存储或本地存储的访问，从而允许您添加，修改或删除存储的数据项。

    • Method Detail

      • length

        long length()
        Returns number of key/value pairs in the storage.
        返回存储中键/值对的数量。
        Returns:
        number of key/value pairs in the storage. Returns 0 if the storage hasn't been initialized yet or has no key/value pairs. 存储中键/值对的数量。如果尚未初始化存储或没有键/值对，则返回0。

      • key

        java.lang.String key(long index)
        Returns the name of the key in the storage. The order of keys is user-agent defined, so you should not rely on it.
        返回存储中键的名称。键的顺序是用户代理定义的，因此您不应依赖它。
        Parameters:
        index - an integer representing the number of the key you want to get the name of. This is a zero-based index. Must be in range 0 < index < length(). -一个整数，代表要获取名称的键的编号。这是从零开始的索引。必须在范围内。
        Returns:
        a string containing the name of the key or null. 包含键或名称的字符串。
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - when the index isn't in 0 < index < length() range.

      • setItem

        boolean setItem(java.lang.String key,
                java.lang.String value)
        Adds the key and value to the storage, or updates key's value if it already exists.
        将密钥和值添加到存储中，或更新密钥的值（如果已存在）。
        Parameters:
        key - the name of the key you want to create/update. Cannot be null. -您要创建/更新的密钥的名称。不可能是 。
        value - the value you want to give the key you are creating/updating. Cannot be null. -您要提供要创建/更新的密钥的值。不可能是 。
        Returns:
        true if key/value pair was successfully added or updated. Returns false in case of exceptions. 键/值对是否已成功添加或更新。在有异常的情况下返回。
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - when the key or value is null.

      • clear

        boolean clear()
        Removes all key/value pairs in the storage.
        删除存储中的所有键/值对。
        Returns:
        true if storage was successfully cleared. Returns false in case of exceptions or storage was not initialized. 是否成功清除存储。如果发生异常或未初始化存储，则返回。
